22:14.179 --> 22:15.840
<i>-Hi, boss.
-Hi.</i>

22:16.015 --> 22:18.040
<i>-How are you? lt's not too late--
-No.</i>

22:18.851 --> 22:21.115
l'm fine. lt's fine.
Hold on just a second.

22:21.286 --> 22:22.344
Okay.

22:27.626 --> 22:30.993
Hey. Thanks so much for calling.

22:31.730 --> 22:34.756
l can't sleep. l don't know
what got into me this morning.

22:34.933 --> 22:37.401
l have never taken a swat
at anybody.

22:37.569 --> 22:39.560
Well, l do know. l'm pregnant.

22:39.938 --> 22:41.929
You're preg-- You're pregnant!

22:42.641 --> 22:46.042
Yeah. Secret's out.

22:46.445 --> 22:48.504
<i>You're pregnant!</i>

22:48.681 --> 22:50.410
l had a hunch.

22:58.257 --> 23:00.691
That guy that picks you up
sometimes, Al?

23:01.226 --> 23:02.750
Oh, you noticed Al.

23:02.961 --> 23:05.225
He lights up every time
he sees you.

23:05.497 --> 23:06.930
<i>So good, huh?</i>

23:07.099 --> 23:09.693
<i>He's great. He's just
been out of work lately.</i>

23:09.868 --> 23:12.530
So we've just been
marathon worrying.

23:12.705 --> 23:15.697
So l'm not myself lately.
So when your father--

23:15.874 --> 23:17.364
Oh, don't worry about it.

23:18.310 --> 23:22.076
So did you tell Terry
about what happened to you?

23:22.815 --> 23:24.373
l'd rather not get into that.

23:24.550 --> 23:27.144
<i>She bailed? You should go call...</i>

23:27.319 --> 23:31.119
...another girl. Distract yourself.
Right?

23:31.423 --> 23:33.482
Forward motion.

23:34.226 --> 23:36.421
